{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5756b290eb","title":"关于科学奖金和学衔的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"549b46971c","index":0,"year":1960,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"5756b290eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958.1-1960）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji43","name":"毛泽东全集第43卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/43-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"66a14fda07","type":"paragraph","text":"在上海会上的融斋（摘要）","index":0,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"d51658de4e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六〇年一月）一月九日","index":1,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"15c234551e","type":"paragraph","text":"人类历史一百来万年中，资产阶级统治的三百年是一个大跃进。资产阶级都能够实现大跃进，无产阶级为什么不能实现大跃进？现在，有些人不相信我们，是有理由的。你没有东西，人家怎么能够相信呢？要人家糊里糊涂相信我们，这是不能设想的。经过若干年，我们正有了东西，而且经过多次反复，他们才会相信我们。","index":2,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"abb47e91d6","type":"paragraph","text":"兴","index":3,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"d79adcddb2","type":"paragraph","text":"深","index":4,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"101e680bbe","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":5,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"6d61e4b040","type":"paragraph","text":"茶","index":6,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"2790e28add","type":"paragraph","text":"要长期保持大跃进，必须搞好工农业的比例关系。这一套两条腿走路中间，工农业的比例关系是最主要的。","index":7,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"6a8509b6c3","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十七日","index":8,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"c07a4279c8","type":"paragraph","text":"我们能够管的六亿多人口，其他地方我们都管不了。有些地方有我们的使馆，可以进行一切可以进行的活动，但是，也不等于我们能够当他们的参谋长。我们不能当美、英的参谋长，也不能当苏联的参谋长。要分几个阶段，我们的国家搞强大起来，我们的人民搞进步起来，争取我们的经济接近美国和苏联那个时候的水平。这主要靠自己把工作做好。我们的工作重点是争取人民，包括工人、农民、革命知识分子、革命的民族资产阶级。","index":9,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"47019dda9c","type":"paragraph","text":"关于科学奖金和学衡的指示","index":10,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"b8733f78b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六〇年一月）","index":11,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"d36769f57d","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林奖金我们没有就不要搞，追逐个人名利地位的事不要搞。我们打了那么多年仗还不是把蒋介石那个特级上将打倒了。勋章、博士那些东西不要搞了。","index":12,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"76e2df43aa","type":"paragraph","text":"使官主义走向它的反面","index":13,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"b4fd67d6de","type":"paragraph","text":"对一个文件的批语","index":14,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"449fcb4586","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六〇年春）","index":15,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"6ed4618304","type":"paragraph","text":"积极方面是形势大好，这是主要的。消极方面，突出的表现是五多、五少。就是说，会议多，联系群众少；文件表报多，经验总结少：事务多，学习少：一般号召多，细致的组织","index":16,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb"}],"page":{"id":"1dae45e92a","publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"5756b290eb","start":270,"end":270}},"maoquanji43":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"851578e156","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林奖金我们没有就不要搞，追逐个人名利地位的事不要搞。我们打了那么多年仗还不是把蒋介石那个特级上将打倒了。勋章、博士那些东西不要搞了","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5756b290eb"},{"id":"c2f784de60","type":"title","text":"关于科学奖金和学衔的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5756b290eb"}],"page":{"id":"4afdedf4a3","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5756b290eb","start":130,"end":130}}}},"__N_SSG":true}